Power, wealth, immortality, Galeb has had it all. He's one of the oldest and most feared vampires in Boston. And yet, he's grasping for something that's lost. Or perhaps it was never there to begin with.

Play as 3 heroes in VtM: Swansong, coming to the Epic Games Store in 2022!

Welcome to the world of Zenozoik. Explore this strange land as Pseudo, a powerful warrior on a quest to obtain the Artifacts of Chaos.

There is only one law in Zenozoik: a deadly game of dice that decides the rules of engagement. Obey these rules in brutal hand-to-hand combat.

node.text: Take on the lethal and evolving Archaen threat in Rainbow Six Extraction. New gear, new abilities, new strategy.
